        <updateDate>2020-07-02T18:30:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Bailouts for Illegal Aliens Act</b></p> <p>This bill withholds funding authorized under the Coronavirus Aid, Relief, and Economic Security Act (CARES Act) from any state or municipality that provides relief payments through a program targeted exclusively to individuals who are believed to be unlawfully present in the United States.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
